{"tid":1674779,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連續拳打男子13次的士司機認罪囚5個月2星期","createTime":"2019-10-25T11:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T12:04:09.000Z","uid":138409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ddba7b83924897868dc1e8a755e28882d263ca70","tid":1674779,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488249-20191025.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488249-20191025.htm&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTdT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=2c9c3576\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488249-20191025.htm&h=2a9de7e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488249-20191025.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Vc92ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Vc92ed.jpg&h=8d7da0b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名46歲的士司機7月11日凌晨在淘大花園對開橋底，就撕毁「連儂牆」與現場人士爭執，之後連續拳打一名男子13次，以及襲擊另一名男子，承認兩項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，被判即時監禁5個月2星期。<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官徐綺薇表示，案件並非涉及單一動作，而是連番揮拳，多次拳擊傷者頭部，傷者沒有大礙屬於萬幸，醉酒鬧事並非求情理由，又指即使情緒受示威堵路影響，亦不能在街上當途人為洩憤的工具，認為即時監禁屬於唯一合適的刑罰，考慮被告背景及認罪減刑後，兩項控罪合共判監禁5個月2星期。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告黃堅海在7月11日凌晨零時途經東九龍文化中心地盤外時，因撕下「連儂牆」上便條貼的保護膠，遭附近約15名市民包圍，雙方發生爭執。被告先用右手拳擊一名男子的臉部，再13次拳擊另一名36歲男子。"},{"pid":"a335d0632a512d262c466e6cbed338ce8a5b885e","tid":1674779,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3rZEXN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3rZEXN.gif&h=b0a1f406&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5230ae3d00cf7c4dc86b866ec9ed382ee8b975e3","tid":1674779,"uid":200332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"所謂胸襲判三個月<br />\n十三拳就五個月<br />\n一拳都只係坐十二日..."},{"pid":"f34584b82898ba0fab9cb6adaae851